org.eclipse.egf.pattern
Interface Pattern

All Superinterfaces:
Generator
All Known Implementing Classes:
PatternImpl
public interface Pattern
extends Generator

A representation of the model object 'Pattern'.

The following features are supported:

  • Id
  • Short Id
  • Logical Name
  • Description
  • Relations
  • Parameters
  • Call Parameters

See Also:
